Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.22,0:00:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立直
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.39,0:00:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.57,0:00:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点和  1300
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.91,0:00:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是快速过庄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.87,0:00:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这样的比赛中四次里能和一次已经不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.02,0:00:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也是可以接受的吧
